node.text: When we get all our kids together...my life is beyond awesome!
My immediate clan +uncle greg all together...it doesn’t get any better!!

Festa dei sette pesci ( feast of the seven fishes) our Italian American Christmas Eve Feast is as much fun cooking it as it is eating !🎄Scallops, Alaskan smoked salmon, grilled red snapper & octopus, stuffed calamari @davidroccosvita , sautéed shrimp & clams🍷

Let the holidays begin! My kind of appetizer with a very different and delicious #mátétoscana #merlot followed by tonights main course of mussels paired with my favorite #blancdeblancs #napa from @stralavineyards
The beginning of a new generation...my first selfie with my first grandson... congrats to my Megan and son in law Matt who have blessed us this Christmas with William Bennett! Salute!🍷

Back from a quick weekend with in-laws in Salt Lake and need an easy dinner..quick sauce with Italian sausage and (im not embarrassed to say packaged #Rana ravs they are the best packaged ravioli) fresh garlic bread and my current fav reserve chianti #antinori 🍷#alwaysgoidtobehomecooking
Pesce all puttanesca using halibut my sister in law caught in Alaska..perfect with my current favorite #villaantinori #chianticlassico ..recipe compliments of @davidroccosvita

My wife  always kicks my butt on making a healthy meal..tonight was jalapeño/mango alaskan salmon tacos! So fresh tasting.. simple mango salsa with baked salmon (thanks to @akmzfitz for the fresh alaskan salmon) and butter lettuce leaf wrap in a corn tortilla.

Olives harvested in Tuscany in October and the oil in my house December 3! Thanks to our friends @cretaiole Look forward to being there at next years harvest🍷 #kidsstockingstuffers #toscana #olio #pienza
Thanksgiving & Christmas tradition since I can remember at my Uncles #castagne🌰 #openfire Happy Thanksgiving 🦃!!
Love clean out the fridge risotto..asparagus & mushrooms with a killer #etnabianco from @cusumanowinery perfect match!
Most inexpensive meal for a family this Tuscan Peposo made with stew meat, pepper, salt, tomato sauce and chianti ..so few ingredients such a big flavor.. recipe @davidroccosvita

Good morning #oregon #mthood its going to be a glorious day! Believe it or not there is no color enhancement here! This is what you get with iphone 11 and God! Thanks to our hosts @rubyvineyard for a great stay and awesome #pinotnoir #chardonnay
Great last minute trip to the #willamettevalley and #oregon coast to taste some delicious #pinotnoir and have some dad and son time🍷
Some of my favorite memories are with the family in Florence..memories for life!#piazzaperuzzi #firenze #tbt #moretocome #massimo #mm

It doesn’t get more healthier than this butternut squash soup: butternut squash/apples/sautéed onions a little cumin , blend and done! Delicious with an awesome red blend from #napavalley squash recipe @davidroccosvita

When I cook for my dad and he looks up from the plate and just says “delicious” ...I have succeeded...tonight linguini alle vongole with a spectacular #vermentino #bolgheri #antinori  did the trick. Thanks @davidroccosvita
Nothing left of my olives😭after all the critters helped themselves but they sure are pretty!
Was a great year visiting #napavalley & #sonoma ..our hearts go out to all of you and hope you keep safe!

Simple pappardelle & mushroom (added sprig of nepitella) dish with a #tenutadelleterrenere #etnarosso perfect pair🍷Thanks to @lidiabastianich for the recipe and #pbs #wttw for airing real cooking shows.
My dad’s favorite dish is bolognese and mine is eggplant parmigiana..today I made us both happy for Sunday supper using bolognese sauce in my eggplant parm 🍆 🍷win win!!
Still time to eat fresh garden veggies with pasta mare e monti di peppe from @davidroccosvita  recipe🍷molto fresca !
Chilly night calls for comfort food with this delicious goulash from Friuli-Venezia along an Amarone della Valpolicella 🍷
Always a great ride @united #sunsetsundays

Great weekend with my kids enjoying the fall harvest in #napavalley and the lobster 🦞 fest/grape stomping contest @sequoiagrove Fantastic party!
Also a big thanks to our friends Laura & Jason for sharing their delicious wine with us!🍷#missingmegmattkev
